Title: S10:E4 - Building a personal brand early in your development career (Amy Chen)
Description: We chat with Amy Chen, systems software engineer at VMware and creator of the Amy Codes YouTube channel, about her career two years into being a professional developer, getting into coding for distributed systems, and the benefits of creating a personal brand.
